EDUCATIONAL USE NOTICE:

This project is developed for educational purposes as part of the Winter School 2025
curriculum on Economic & Social Crises in Palestine and Morocco. All datasets included
are synthetic, aggregated, or publicly available data used for teaching purposes only.

Students and instructors are encouraged to:
- Use this software for learning and teaching
- Modify and extend the dashboards
- Share improvements with the community
- Cite appropriately when using in academic work

For questions or contributions, please contact the course instructors.
